{"id":"api/common/CurrencyPipe","title":"CurrencyPipe","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/CurrencyPipe\", \"name\": \"CurrencyPipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L183-L305\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"currencypipe\">CurrencyPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4nrwnc3k470e50q7nufo16ek0\">将数字转换为货币字符串，根据确定组大小和分隔符、小数点字符和其他特定于区域设置的配置的区域设置规则进行格式化。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n<section class=\"pipe-overview\">\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">{{ value_expression | <span class=\"kwd nocode\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a></span> [ : currencyCode [ : display [ : digitsInfo [ : locale ] ] ] ] }}</code-example>\n\n  \n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\">\n      <code>CommonModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  <h2 id=\"input-value\">输入值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#input-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6y18uxg2a2xx1qj04ok4glp0s\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>value</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6ygb982tr2uhssnms63pb73qq\">要格式化为货币的数字。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h2 id=\"parameters\">参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#parameters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9tn04biywgwi9nxlyk32mxr13\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>currencyCode</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"43lqifhtr2tazxdo7xstda3sw\">可选值。默认值为 <code>this._defaultCurrencyCode</code>。</p>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>this._defaultCurrencyCode</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bqzthyvt3n7lc6mc5cpiq5fwp\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>display</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | boolean</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aira2ce5umheeppefmhx1739c\">货币指示器的格式。以下之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4o1e1fnq35smwvfdaw6fu57ql\"><code>code</code>：显示代码（例如 <code>USD</code>）。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1gwovcwow3zlbazw0scos29q\"><code>symbol</code>（默认）：显示符号（例如 <code>$</code>）。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6gog0lwzf6i10x0z8to7kzf7p\"><code>symbol-narrow</code>：对有两个货币符号的区域设置使用窄符号。例如，加元 CAD 的符号是 <code>CA$</code> 和符号-narrow <code>$</code>。如果此区域设置没有窄符号，则使用此区域设置的标准符号。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"deblgjokri4puar5va5zq9fe6\">字符串：使用给定的字符串值，而不是代码或符号。例如，空字符串将抑制货币 &amp; 符号。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5361xpvdtdrvqfc7enfb63yup\">布尔值（在 v5 中标记为已弃用）：symbol 为 <code>true</code>，<code>code</code> 为 false。</li>\n</ul>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>'symbol'</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"30gid03dkl55k2oxbmk61drmu\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>digitsInfo</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9fu06t45wkkjzckxe56u6wbzh\">十进制表示选项，由以下格式的字符串指定：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"94vtyn87wy2x8mdcq9mux6l3n\"><code>minIntegerDigits</code>：小数点前的最小整数位数。默认为 <code>1</code>。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"k17pjs6jwvghq1jy4f7xt0wl\"><code>minFractionDigits</code>：小数点后的最小位数。默认为 <code>2</code>。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"92wzfixxnzy6zt5eq5e73ckx9\"><code>maxFractionDigits</code>：小数点后的最大位数。默认为 <code>2</code>。如果未提供，则该数字将根据<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a>指定的内容使用适当的位数格式化。例如，加元有 2 位，而智利比索没有。</li>\n</ul>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6cuhpqqkoxc2njmr3u8ccohar\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locale</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"afrzjhsxuuayf4aj41948q9pp\">可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/getCurrencySymbol\"><code>getCurrencySymbol</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/formatCurrency\"><code>formatCurrency</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"apxusl1k3ktgjapum5x8agd89\">以下代码显示了管道如何根据各种格式规范将数字转换为文本字符串，其中调用者的默认区域设置是 <code>en-US</code>。</p>\n<code-example path=\"common/pipes/ts/currency_pipe.ts\" region=\"CurrencyPipe\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'currency-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;!--output '$0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{ a | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a> }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CA$0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{ a | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>: 'CAD' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CAD0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{ a | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>: 'CAD' : 'code' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CA$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{ b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>: 'CAD' : 'symbol' : '4.2-2' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{ b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>: 'CAD' : 'symbol-narrow' : '4.2-2' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '0&nbsp;001,35&nbsp;CA$'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{ b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>: 'CAD' : 'symbol' : '4.2-2' : 'fr' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CLP1' because CLP has no cents--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{ b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>: 'CLP' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;`,\n})\nexport class CurrencyPipeComponent {\n  a: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/pipes-overview\n - guide/pipes-transform-data\n - start/start-data\n - start/start-forms\n - start/start-routing\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#input-value\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#parameters\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#see-also\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#usage-notes\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#导出自\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/common/getCurrencySymbol\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/DEFAULT_CURRENCY_CODE\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L183-L305\n-->"}